text: Imad Mohammad Deeb Khamis (; born 1 August 1961) is a Syrian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Syria from 2016 to 2020 under President Bashar al- Assad. He was Minister of Electricity from 2011 to 2016. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Syria
title: Imad Khamis
